1
00:00:57,400 --> 00:00:58,160
Sister,

2
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:01,210
you came into my room late at night.

3
00:01:01,480 --> 00:01:03,340
Are you trying to steal my things?

4
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:06,680
You are always like this, sister.

5
00:01:06,680 --> 00:01:08,880
If not stealing, then robbing.

6
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:10,400
Are you really

7
00:01:11,039 --> 00:01:12,840
that obsessed with my things?

8
00:01:15,440 --> 00:01:16,840
I returned to my own home.

9
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,240
Why would I steal?

10
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:19,560
Why would I rob?

11
00:01:20,360 --> 00:01:22,000
You killed Aunt Qin,

12
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:24,640
stole the Yaowang Valley map,

13
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:26,760
and Aunt Qin's medical book.

14
00:01:27,440 --> 00:01:28,440
It is you, sister,

15
00:01:28,720 --> 00:01:30,980
who always takes other people's things.

16
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:33,720
Who is coveting whose things?

17
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,320
Your husband is here.

18
00:01:44,039 --> 00:01:45,370
Where did my husband go?

19
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:47,920
Who are you talking to, my wife?

20
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:50,960
Why does it sound like

21
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:53,360
you're not the only one in this room?

22
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:55,690
I am entertaining a distinguished guest.

23
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:58,759
I am holding a matchlock to her head.

24
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:01,920
Her life or death is at my whim.

25
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:05,620
Who is worth such anger from you, my wife?

26
00:02:06,240 --> 00:02:07,970
Of course, it's my good sister,

27
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:09,840
Yan Qingshu.

28
00:02:13,320 --> 00:02:14,200
Could it be

29
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,570
that you know her, Husband?

30
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,650
You must be joking, my wife.

31
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:21,090
I am just a blind man.

32
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,560
How could I know Miss Yan?

33
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:24,480
That's right.

34
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:27,000
I forgot my husband is blind.

35
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,280
Sister,

36
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:30,000
do you know

37
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:33,360
tonight is my wedding with Xie Yuheng?

38
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:36,960
Aren't you marrying me tonight, my wife?

39
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:40,040
Who is Xie Yuheng?

40
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:40,960
Enough.

41
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:45,840
Xie Yuheng,

42
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:48,380
how long are you going to keep acting?

43
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:50,760
You lied to me and played me for a fool.

44
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:53,920
You are a complete liar.

45
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:54,720
Mingli,

46
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,480
when did you find out?

47
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:58,360
Guess.

48
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,880
Am I not as stupid

49
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,300
as you thought?

50
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:04,480
Mingli, let me explain.

51
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,920
I am truly repentant this time.

52
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:10,120
I sincerely want to grow old with you.

53
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:10,960
Your sincerity

54
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:13,040
is to use your identity as the son-in-law of the Duke's Mansion

55
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:14,680
to pave the way for the Xie family,

56
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:18,210
and to vainly attempt to revive your family's glory through me.

57
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:20,320
You bastard,

58
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:21,840
dream on.

59
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,600
This matchlock

60
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:28,160
was specially prepared for you.

61
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,920
You will definitely like this way of dying.

62
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:34,640
Does it hurt?

63
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:38,770
But it's not even a ten-thousandth of how you hurt me.

64
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:40,680
Spare me,

65
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,280
Mingli.

66
00:03:44,079 --> 00:03:45,880
Everything before was my fault.

67
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:46,860
From now on,

68
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:49,820
I will definitely treat you with sincerity.

69
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,240
Mingli,

70
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,340
believe your Brother Yuheng.

71
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:54,380
Sincerity,

72
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:56,770
I don't want it anymore.

73
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:58,600
Now I

74
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:01,160
As long as I am happy.

75
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:13,580
Don't kill me, Mingli.

76
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:16,730
For the sake of our past relationship.

77
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:20,959
Our past makes me even more disgusted.

78
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:08,640
Xie Yuheng.

79
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:10,800
I'm finally rid of you.

80
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:12,760
It's over.

81
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:15,600
It's all over.

82
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:44,800
At first, the poisoned person

83
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:47,440
will feel weak

84
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:49,570
and cough up blood constantly.

85
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:55,000
Then they will become emaciated, and their organs will feel like they are burning.

86
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,580
Their meridians will be blocked,

87
00:05:58,080 --> 00:05:59,880
and their pupils will turn gray,

88
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,280
until

89
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,890
their face looks like a corpse,

90
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:06,490
and their hair turns white as snow.

91
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:10,280
Changxiangwang.

92
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:15,520
The secret Beidi poison, Changxiangwang,

93
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:18,720
is extremely treacherous, odorless, and tasteless.

94
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:21,380
Mixed in food, it only shows symptoms over time.

95
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:24,960
It erodes a person's vitality, resembling tuberculosis.

96
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:26,960
It is often misdiagnosed by doctors.

97
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:29,320
However, due to the treacherous nature of this poison,

98
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:31,850
no solution can be found in any medical texts.

99
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:34,840
Once it penetrates the bone marrow,

100
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,720
those in the middle to late stages

101
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:38,600
will not live past a year.

102
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:45,800
The pulse is deep, sluggish, and faint like smoke.

103
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:48,920
It is exactly the sign that the poison has entered the bone marrow,

104
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,320
and is beyond a cure.

105
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,760
One year.

106
00:06:58,840 --> 00:07:00,370
I only have one year to live.

107
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:05,160
The grievances of the Xiao and Yan families

108
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,800
have not been cleared.

109
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:08,920
Xiaotao.

110
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:10,800
Xiaowu.

111
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:12,360
Aunt Qin.

112
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,240
Liu Sanniang.

113
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,930
These vengeances have yet to be taken.

114
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:22,760
I cannot die.

115
00:07:25,080 --> 00:07:26,120
I cannot die.

116
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:33,680
I cannot die before my enemies.

117
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:42,090
Right Wise King,

118
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,200
I have come as agreed.

119
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:48,159
Ceding two northern cities, opening border markets,

120
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,580
and doubling the annual tribute.

121
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:54,480
This is the utmost sincerity of Dafeng.

122
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:57,320
Two cities?

123
00:07:58,520 --> 00:08:00,980
Are you dismissing refugees, Your Majesty?

124
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:02,640
I want ten cities.

125
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:07,480
How dare you raise your demands!

126
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,640
Not one less.

127
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:11,080
Along the northern border,

128
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:13,000
ten cities including Tongguan.

129
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:14,200
Otherwise,

130
00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:18,760
don't blame the wolves under my command

131
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:21,690
for trampling your Dafeng border.

132
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,480
Insolent!

133
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:26,330
Do you really think I wouldn't dare keep you here?

134
00:08:31,840 --> 00:08:33,280
Calm down, Your Majesty.

135
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,440
Killing me is easy.

136
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:36,919
But,

137
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:40,039
if certain things

138
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:43,000
are made public...

139
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:46,040
We'd be in big trouble.

140
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:57,010
You recognize this, right?

141
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:05,720
If the people of the world knew

142
00:09:05,760 --> 00:09:08,880
that the Emperor of Dafeng actually encouraged the prince

143
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:10,600
to privately manufacture weapons,

144
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,760
and used the Empress Dowager's seal

145
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:15,050
to trade with enemy countries,

146
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,800
could you still sit securely

147
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,440
on your throne?

148
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,840
How dare you threaten me!

149
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:26,800
Ten cities

150
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:30,680
in exchange for the eternal stability of your empire.

151
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:32,820
It's not a bad deal.

152
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,040
Ten cities.

153
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:47,800
I will give them to you.

154
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:49,000
Your Majesty is wise.

155
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:55,800
Then may our two countries be allied forever.

156
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,200
Farewell.

157
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:05,280
What a move by Cui Tingru,

158
00:10:06,760 --> 00:10:08,690
to actually set a death trap for me.

159
00:10:12,040 --> 00:10:12,760
Di dogs.

160
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:16,250
The humiliation today,

161
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:20,880
will be repaid a hundredfold in the future.

162
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:45,640
Second Miss,

163
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,320
what are your orders?

164
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:50,930
Deliver this letter

165
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:53,320
to Yan Qingshu.

166
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,000
Yes,

167
00:10:58,280 --> 00:10:59,680
I... I will go right away.

168
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:23,570
Coming here alone, Sister,

169
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:25,240
is truly admirable.

170
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:28,000
Our personal grudges

171
00:11:28,640 --> 00:11:30,170
shouldn't involve others.

172
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:32,000
Are you blaming me, Sister?

173
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:35,560
Blaming me for killing Liu Sanniang,

174
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:37,120
Madam Qin,

175
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:39,480
and Xiaotao?

176
00:11:40,640 --> 00:11:44,170
You borrowed the blade of the Beidi royal family to take my life.

177
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:46,040
The one who killed Xiaotao

178
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:47,640
is you.

179
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:49,400
Who else?

180
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:52,880
Did you think it was the Xies,

181
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:54,200
and the Prince of Ling?

182
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:57,040
Of course, they also wanted to kill you.

183
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:59,400
I merely went along with the flow.

184
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:01,160
Yan Mingli,

185
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:04,800
today, in front of our father's tombstone,

186
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:06,330
I will ask you one last time.

187
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:09,680
You've killed so many innocent people.

188
00:12:10,040 --> 00:12:11,570
Have you ever felt remorse?

189
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:16,040
If I repent,

190
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:18,680
can they come back to life?

191
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,160
Yan Qingshu,

192
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,960
sorry to keep you waiting today.

193
00:12:46,880 --> 00:12:47,720
Yan Qingshu,

194
00:12:48,560 --> 00:12:50,360
you actually set an ambush here!

195
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:51,160
Qingshu!

196
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:54,120
Treating you in your own way,

197
00:12:54,520 --> 00:12:56,600
