198
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:58,080
You bitch!

199
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:02,800
If it weren't for your hypocritical kindness and hidden malice,

200
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:04,440
if you hadn't bullied me for being born of a concubine,

201
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:06,680
humiliated my mother, and stolen my love,

202
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:08,080
would I have come to this?

203
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:10,130
My ending up like this today

204
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:11,720
is all forced by you!

205
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:13,960
So what if you are born of a concubine?

206
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:15,520
So what if you are born of the legal wife?

207
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:17,040
Even if your surname wasn't Yan,

208
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:18,300
