211
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:22,800
Father, she admitted it!

212
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:25,360
She never accepted us!

213
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:26,880
Normally,

214
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:28,720
