215
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,720
In reality,

216
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:31,720
it's all hypocrisy.

217
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:34,240
She never gave me and my mother any dignity!

218
00:13:34,520 --> 00:13:35,400
Yan Qingshu,

219
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:37,600
