220
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:39,380
What right do you have?

221
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,480
What right do you have to live such a glamorous life?

222
00:13:41,480 --> 00:13:42,740
What right do you have?

223
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:45,720
Whether I am good or evil, human or ghost,

224
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:48,240
is not for you to decide.

225
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,760
But what you owe,

226
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:52,240
