227
00:14:19,760 --> 00:14:22,160
Don't you like using other people's faces?

228
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,600
Then there's no need

229
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:25,320
to keep this face of yours.

230
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:26,960
My face!

231
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,000
My face!

232
00:14:28,680 --> 00:14:29,320
I...

233
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:30,680
My face!

234
00:14:31,160 --> 00:14:31,840
I...

235
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:08,680
Go check over there.

236
00:15:08,680 --> 00:15:09,240
Yes.

237
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:33,000
Found it. It's iron ore.

238
00:15:39,120 --> 00:15:41,120
It seems the Yan family didn't lie.

239
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:47,840
God bless Beidi.

240
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:51,800
Make haste

241
00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:53,840
and deliver this news to the Khan.

242
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:54,360
Yes.

